    <item>
      <title>My Nonsenses are Most Sensible</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/my-nonsenses-are-most-sensible/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/my-nonsenses-are-most-sensible/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5258-My-Nonsenses-are-Most-Sensible.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;My Nonsenses are Most Sensible&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;My Nonsenses is the Most Sensible 
    &lt;div id=&#34;my-nonsenses-is-the-most-sensible&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#my-nonsenses-is-the-most-sensible&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everyone around me seems insane, while I am the only sane one, the only saint! Whatever I do is the right way; whatever you do is senseless, meaningless, illogical.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I smoke in my room, filling it with smoke, and if my family members are disturbed, that&amp;rsquo;s their problem. Tell me, if I can&amp;rsquo;t live my life and smoke in my own room, where on earth should I go?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>My Nonsenses are Most Sensible - Poem</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/my-nonsenses-are-most-sensible-poem/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/my-nonsenses-are-most-sensible-poem/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5258-My-Nonsenses-are-Most-Sensible.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;My Nonsenses are Most Sensible - Poem&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;My Nonsenses is the Most Sensible - Poem 
    &lt;div id=&#34;my-nonsenses-is-the-most-sensible---poem&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#my-nonsenses-is-the-most-sensible---poem&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The world is madness, humans lost in haze,&lt;br&gt;
I stand alone, the saint in this maze.&lt;br&gt;
What I do is right, my path is clear,&lt;br&gt;
Your actions are senseless, driven by fear.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I smoke in my room, my space, my air,&lt;br&gt;
If the smoke bothers others, why should I care?&lt;br&gt;
My lungs, my money, my life to live,&lt;br&gt;
Who are you to take what I won’t give?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>What Is Success?</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/what-is-success/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/what-is-success/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5153-What-Is-Success.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;What Is Success?&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What Is Success? 
    &lt;div id=&#34;what-is-success&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#what-is-success&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A mosquito or flee is roaming around and disturbing you  &lt;br&gt;
You plan to kill it, and you killed it, it is a success.  &lt;br&gt;
An employee is looking for rupees 10000  &lt;br&gt;
for his child’s hospital expenses and  &lt;br&gt;
HR could arrange that finally, it is a success for him.  &lt;br&gt;
A child wants to pass her 5th class exam  &lt;br&gt;
and if she passes it, it is a success.  &lt;br&gt;
If you want to through a used napkin in a dustbin  &lt;br&gt;
and it goes there inside, it is a success.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
